        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4332534376" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16156461756326069627">I worked on this campaign in press advance and met Hunter Thompson while doing so, so this book was a look back at that time. Hunter may have been somewhat crazy but he was a good writer and had fascinating insights, as I recall from the distance of many years.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


